CustomerCreditAlert is a BusinessTask
    owned by ar

    Patterns
        implements ManualTransaction
        implements StaticJava
            is report for ApplicationAdministrator, FinancialsProcessor, FinancialsViewer, ReceivablesManager, ReceivablesAdministrator, ReceivablesSpecialist, CreditAndCollectionSpecialist, Receivables
				category is "Customer"
                report name is "CustomerCreditAlerts"
				Description
					Create a report for customers with a current balance plus open order amount greater than their credit limit.
            Reports
                CustomerCreditAlertReport

    Parameters
        CustGroup               is a CustomerGroup
        CrVarPct                is Numeric size 2
        PctOfLimit              is Numeric size 3

    Parameter Rules
        CustGroup
            required

    Actions
        CustomerCreditAlert is a Set Action
            allow unlimited concurrency
